6. The light absorption film forming apparatus according to claim 5, wherein: 
the evaporating boat includes a central scorching heat area on which the source material is placed for evaporation, a non-wetting area formed at a circumferentially periphery of the scorching heat area, and electrical connector portions extending outward from the non-wetting area; 
wherein the non-wetting area is processed to have a non-wetting property to preclude the source material and the evaporating boat from wetting with respect to one another.

